<module>
	<title>Module Editor</title>
	<description><![CDATA[Editor for local modules.
Building on basic module administration, this module allows you to
- browser local or locally installed modules
- view details of local modules
- edit all attributes of local modules
- uninstall local module</strike>
- import local module to module source</strike>
This module can be extended by:
- Module Installer
- Module Creator
This module needs other modules to be installed:
- Modules (thus Module Sources, App Instances)
]]></description>
